
  TWITTER WEB APPLICATION INSTALLATION OVERVIEW

  Quick Start - Unix
  ------------------

    Make sure perl and make is currently installed.

    $ sudo cpan Dancer
    $ sudo cpan Template
    $ sudo cpan Array::Utils
    $ sudo cpan Net::Twitter
    $ sudo cpan Net::OAuth
    $ sudo cpan IO::Socket::SSL


    To run the app:
    $ ./bin/app.pl

    To access the running app:
    $ http://localhost:3000

    For deployment on Apache server you may visit this url, http://search.cpan.org/dist/Dancer/lib/Dancer/Deployment.pod


  Postscript
  ----------

  To obtain help with installation problems, please email at pjanusc85@gmail.com

  Thanks for using the Twitter Web Application.